                <li>Home  loan</li>
                <li>Car  loan</li>
                <li>Others - eg. personal loan, credit card</li>
              </ul>
          </li>
          
          <li>
              <p><strong>d) Any  lump sum gift to beneficiaries</strong></p>
              <p>Some people wish to be able to give a  lump sum to their loved ones (eg. grandparents, nieces/nephews) or even to  charitable organisation (eg. church, SPCA).<br><br>
                Once completed, you just tally up the  above (a + b + c + d) to determine how much death benefits you require.<br></p>
              <div class="white-box"><p><u>Example</u><br>
              <strong>Total Life Insurance Sum required</strong> = $600,000 + $265,400 =<strong> $865,400</strong></p></div>
